title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Toy maker Hasbro (HAS) has its annual meeting coming up and one investor is pushing for big changes. Analysts say Apple (AAPL) is gearing up to announce major software updates, and could be up for major sports broadcast contracts. Finally, could Universal’s Jurassic World overtake Paramount Global's (NASDAQ:PARA) (NASDAQ:PARAA) Top Gun in the box office?
